title: Ask HN: Which frequently recommended CS/Math books do you absolutely hate?
text:
We have many threads on HN about best books to read in CS or Math. In such threads there are always some popular mentions.

Which such book(s) that are often recommended in online threads that you absolutely hate? Why is your distaste for those books genuine?

title: Ask HN: Where can ASCII Art be Commissioned?
text:
My company would like some ASCII renditions of their logo: https://rainlab.co.jp/en/.

I have waded through old Geocities sites, random ASCII art collections, and various articles; however, 90 percent of URLs are now defunct, and email addresses all get bounced.

I would absolutely love to get in contact with Joan Stark, but my sleuthing skills are unable to escape beyond early 2000s info.

Do you have any brilliant suggestions?
